  "ai_usage": "Use for restaurants, cafés, and bars where the menu is the point. Build category tabs as real buttons toggling panels (aria-selected); render each menu category as a semantic list of dish rows (name, description, dietary markers with text labels, price). Include hours/location and a labeled reservation form. Recolor via the warm tokens; replace dishes. Reduced-motion safe.",
  "path": "effects/website-templates/restaurant-menu.html",
  "source": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\" />\n<title>Restaurant — Interactive Menu</title>\n<script type=\"application/json\" id=\"effect-meta\">\n{\n  \"id\": \"restaurant-menu\",\n  \"title\": \"Restaurant — Interactive Menu\",\n  \"summary\": \"A warm restaurant page with a real, tabbed menu (starters / mains / desserts / drinks), hours, and a reservation form.\",\n  \"description\": \"Unlike a generic landing, this centers the thing diners want: the menu. A warm editorial hero leads into a tabbed menu with dish names, descriptions, dietary dots, and prices, followed by hours/location and a reservation form. Cozy, appetizing, and practical.\",\n  \"theme\": \"website-templates\",\n  \"categories\": [\"template\", \"local\", \"hospitality\"],\n  \"tags\": [\"restaurant\", \"menu\", \"tabs\", \"reservation\", \"food\", \"full-page\"],\n  \"tech\": [\"html\", \"css\", \"js\"],\n  \"era\": \"2020s\",\n  \"difficulty\": \"intermediate\",\n  \"dependencies\": [],\n  \"browser_support\": \"All modern browsers.\",\n  \"performance_notes\": \"A tiny tab toggle + reveals. No images (gradient food tiles). Light.\",\n  \"accessibility_notes\": \"Menu tabs are real buttons with aria-selected and keyboard focus; menu is a semantic list; dietary markers have text labels; reservation uses a labeled form. Reduced-motion safe.\",\n  \"customization\": [\n    { \"name\": \"--paper/--ink/--accent\", \"description\": \"Warm palette\", \"default\": \"cream / espresso / terracotta\" },\n    { \"name\": \"menu data\", \"description\": \"Categories + dishes (name/desc/price)\", \"default\": \"edit markup\" }\n  ],\n  \"variations\": [\"Add prices in two currencies\", \"Wine pairing column\", \"Photo thumbnails per dish\"],\n  \"related\": [\"luxe-serif\", \"organic-wellness\", \"saas-landing\"],\n  \"ai_usage\": \"Use for restaurants, cafés, and bars where the menu is the point. Build category tabs as real buttons toggling panels (aria-selected); render each menu category as a semantic list of dish rows (name, description, dietary markers with text labels, price). Include hours/location and a labeled reservation form. Recolor via the warm tokens; replace dishes. Reduced-motion safe.\"\n}\n</script>\n<style>\n  :root{--paper:#fbf6ee;--paper2:#f3e9da;--ink:#2a1c12;--muted:#806856;--accent:#c0552f;--gold:#b08338;--line:#e6d8c5;\n    --serif:\"Fraunces\",\"Georgia\",serif;--sans:\"Inter\",system-ui,sans-serif;--r:14px;}\n  *{box-sizing:border-box}html{scroll-behavior:smooth}\n  body{margin:0;background:var(--paper);color:var(--ink);font-family:var(--sans);line-height:1.7}\n  a{color:inherit;text-decoration:none}\n  .wrap{max-width:1000px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 1.5rem}\n  nav{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;height:78px}\n  .brand{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:600}\n  .links{display:flex;gap:1.5rem;align-items:center;color:var(--muted);font-size:.92rem}.links a:hover{color:var(--ink)}\n  .btn{background:var(--accent);color:#fff;border:none;border-radius:999px;padding:.65rem 1.4rem;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;transition:transform .15s,filter .15s}\n  .btn:hover{transform:translateY(-2px);filter:brightness(1.05)}\n  .btn.ghost{background:transparent;color:var(--ink);border:1.5px solid var(--accent)}\n  .btn:focus-visible{outline:2px solid var(--gold);outline-offset:3px}\n  .hero{text-align:center;padding:3rem 0 4rem}\n  .ey{color:var(--accent);font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;font-size:.76rem}\n  h1{font-family:var(--serif);font-weight:600;font-size:clamp(2.6rem,7vw,5rem);line-height:1.02;margin:1rem 0 .6rem}\n  h1 em{font-style:italic;color:var(--accent)}\n  .hero p{color:var(--muted);font-size:1.15rem;max-width:46ch;margin:0 auto 1.6rem}\n  .strip{display:flex;gap:.6rem;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:1.4rem}\n  .strip .ph{width:120px;height:84px;border-radius:var(--r)}\n  .p1{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#e9a23b,#c0552f)}.p2{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#7a8b4f,#46603a)}.p3{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#c45d6e,#8a3b52)}.p4{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#caa05a,#8a6a2f)}\n  section{padding:3.5rem 0}\n  h2{font-family:var(--serif);font-weight:600;font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);text-align:center;margin:0 0 1.6rem}\n  .tabs{display:flex;gap:.5rem;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:2rem}\n  .tab{background:var(--paper2);border:1px solid var(--line);color:var(--muted);border-radius:999px;padding:.5rem 1.2rem;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;font-family:var(--serif)}\n  .tab[aria-selected=\"true\"]{background:var(--accent);color:#fff;border-color:transparent}\n  .tab:focus-visible{outline:2px solid var(--gold);outline-offset:2px}\n  .cat{display:none;max-width:760px;margin:0 auto}.cat.on{display:block}\n  .dish{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr auto;gap:.4rem 1rem;padding:1.1rem 0;border-bottom:1px dashed var(--line)}\n  .dish h3{font-family:var(--serif);font-weight:600;margin:0;font-size:1.25rem;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.5rem}\n  .dot{font-size:.7rem;padding:.1rem .45rem;border-radius:999px;border:1px solid var(--line);color:var(--muted);font-family:var(--sans)}\n  .v{color:#5f7a3a;border-color:#cfe0b5}.gf{color:#9a6a2f;border-color:#ecd9b5}\n  .price{font-family:var(--serif);font-weight:600;color:var(--accent);font-size:1.2rem}\n  .desc{grid-column:1;color:var(--muted);font-size:.95rem;margin:0}\n  .info{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:2.5rem;background:var(--paper2);border-radius:24px;padding:2.5rem;align-items:center}\n  .info h2{text-align:left;margin:0 0 .6rem}\n  .hours{list-style:none;padding:0;margin:0}.hours li{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);padding:.5rem 0;color:var(--muted)}\n  form{display:grid;gap:.7rem}\n  form input,form select{padding:.75rem;border-radius:10px;border:1px solid var(--line);background:var(--paper);color:var(--ink);font-family:inherit}\n  footer{border-top:1px solid var(--line);color:var(--muted);text-align:center;padding:2.4rem 0;font-size:.9rem}\n  .reveal{opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px);transition:opacity .6s,transform .6s ease}.reveal.in{opacity:1;transform:none}\n  @media(max-width:760px){.info{grid-template-columns:1fr}.links a:not(.btn){display:none}}\n  @media(prefers-reduced-motion:reduce){.reveal{opacity:1;transform:none;transition:none}html{scroll-behavior:auto}}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <div class=\"wrap\">\n    <nav>\n      <div class=\"brand\">Saffron &amp; Salt</div>\n      <div class=\"links\"><a href=\"#menu\">Menu</a><a href=\"#visit\">Visit</a><a href=\"#book\">Book</a><a class=\"btn\" href=\"#book\">Reserve</a></div>\n    </nav>\n\n    <header class=\"hero\">\n      <p class=\"ey\">Modern Mediterranean · est. 2019</p>\n      <h1>Cooked with <em>fire</em>,<br>served with love.</h1>\n      <p>A neighborhood kitchen built around the wood oven, the season, and the long table.</p>\n      <a class=\"btn\" href=\"#book\">Reserve a table</a>\n      <div class=\"strip\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"ph p1\"></span><span class=\"ph p2\"></span><span class=\"ph p3\"></span><span class=\"ph p4\"></span></div>\n    </header>\n  </div>\n\n  <section id=\"menu\"><div class=\"wrap\">\n    <h2 class=\"reveal\">The Menu</h2>\n    <div class=\"tabs\" role=\"tablist\" aria-label=\"Menu categories\">\n      <button class=\"tab\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"true\" data-cat=\"starters\">Starters</button>\n      <button class=\"tab\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" data-cat=\"mains\">Mains</button>\n      <button class=\"tab\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" data-cat=\"desserts\">Desserts</button>\n      <button class=\"tab\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" data-cat=\"drinks\">Drinks</button>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"cat on\" data-cat=\"starters\">\n      <div class=\"dish\"><h3>Charred flatbread <span class=\"dot v\">veg</span></h3><span class=\"price\">$9</span><p class=\"desc\">Wood oven, za'atar, whipped feta, wild honey.</p></div>\n      <div class=\"dish\"><h3>Burrata &amp; peaches</h3><span class=\"price\">$14</span><p class=\"desc\">Grilled stone fruit, basil oil, aged balsamic.</p></div>\n      <div class=\"dish\"><h3>Smoked eggplant <span class=\"dot v\">veg</span> <span class=\"dot gf\">gf</span></h3><span class=\"price\">$11</span><p class=\"desc\">Tahini, pomegranate, toasted pine nuts.</p></div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"cat\" data-cat=\"mains\">\n      <div class=\"dish\"><h3>Lamb shoulder</h3><span class=\"price\">$28</span><p class=\"desc\">Slow-cooked 12 hours, charred onion, jus.</p></div>\n      <div class=\"dish\"><h3>Line-caught sea bass <span class=\"dot gf\">gf</span></h3><span class=\"price\">$26</span><p class=\"desc\">Salsa verde, fennel, new potatoes.</p></div>\n      <div class=\"dish\"><h3>Roast cauliflower steak <span class=\"dot v\">veg</span></h3><span class=\"price\">$19</span><p class=\"desc\">Romesco, capers, golden raisins.</p></div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"cat\" data-cat=\"desserts\">\n      <div class=\"dish\"><h3>Olive oil cake</h3><span class=\"price\">$10</span><p class=\"desc\">Citrus, crème fraîche, candied zest.</p></div>\n      <div class=\"dish\"><h3>Dark chocolate tart <span class=\"dot gf\">gf</span></h3><span class=\"price\">$11</span><p class=\"desc\">Sea salt, smoked almond praline.</p></div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"cat\" data-cat=\"drinks\">\n      <div class=\"dish\"><h3>Natural wine (glass)</h3><span class=\"price\">$12</span><p class=\"desc\">Ask for today's short, lovely list.</p></div>\n      <div class=\"dish\"><h3>Saffron spritz</h3><span class=\"price\">$13</span><p class=\"desc\">House aperitivo, citrus, soda.</p></div>\n      <div class=\"dish\"><h3>Mint &amp; lime soda <span class=\"dot v\">veg</span></h3><span class=\"price\">$6</span><p class=\"desc\">Cold-pressed, lightly sweet.</p></div>\n    </div>\n  </div></section>\n\n  <section id=\"visit\"><div class=\"wrap\"><div class=\"info reveal\">\n    <div>\n      <h2>Visit us</h2>\n      <p style=\"color:var(--muted)\">128 Harbour Lane, Old Town. Walk-ins welcome at the bar; tables by reservation.</p>\n      <ul class=\"hours\">\n        <li><span>Tue–Thu</span><span>5pm – 10pm</span></li>\n        <li><span>Fri–Sat</span><span>5pm – 11pm</span></li>\n        <li><span>Sunday</span><span>12pm – 9pm (brunch)</span></li>\n        <li><span>Monday</span><span>Closed</span></li>\n      </ul>\n    </div>\n    <form id=\"book\" onsubmit=\"event.preventDefault();this.querySelector('button').textContent='Requested ✓'\">\n      <h2 style=\"font-size:1.6rem\">Book a table</h2>\n      <input placeholder=\"Name\" aria-label=\"Name\" required>\n      <input type=\"date\" aria-label=\"Date\" required>\n      <select aria-label=\"Party size\"><option>2 guests</option><option>3 guests</option><option>4 guests</option><option>5+ guests</option></select>\n      <button class=\"btn\" type=\"submit\">Request reservation</button>\n    </form>\n  </div></div></section>\n\n  <footer>© <span id=\"yr\"></span> Saffron &amp; Salt · 128 Harbour Lane · (555) 010-7788</footer>\n  </div>\n  <script>\n    document.getElementById('yr').textContent=new Date().getFullYear();\n    var tabs=[].slice.call(document.querySelectorAll('.tab'));\n    tabs.forEach(function(t){t.addEventListener('click',function(){\n      tabs.forEach(function(x){x.setAttribute('aria-selected','false')}); t.setAttribute('aria-selected','true');\n      document.querySelectorAll('.cat').forEach(function(c){c.classList.toggle('on',c.dataset.cat===t.dataset.cat)});\n    });});\n    var io=new IntersectionObserver(function(es){es.forEach(function(e){if(e.isIntersecting){e.target.classList.add('in');io.unobserve(e.target)}})},{threshold:.12});\n    document.querySelectorAll('.reveal').forEach(function(el){io.observe(el)});\n  </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"
}
